{"word":"πλησίστιος","slug":"πλησίστιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πλησίστιος</b></el> <el>(πλης-ίστιος, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πίμπλημι'><el>πίμπλημι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>filling the sails</i>, <el>οὖρος</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <i>with full sails</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}